In conclusion, Your Honor, I plead guilty to the offense of accepting a bribe. I acknowledge the seriousness of my actions and the harm they may have caused. I ask the court for leniency and the opportunity to make amends. I am ready to accept any consequences that may come as a result of my actions and will strive to become a better member of society moving forward.

